view.dialogLoader

Class ClassGUIDialogLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.dialogLoader.ClassGUIDialogLoader

  • public class ClassGUIDialogLoader
extends java.lang.Object

    ClassGUIDialogLoader

    A dialog loader (provided with an active shell) that dynamicly loads class's fields to a form(Booleans are translated as checkboxes). On submit returns an instance of that class
